  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Warehouseman",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>NAIGAI NITTO SINGAPORE PTE LTD, established in Singapore in 1979, is a whole subsidiary of Naigai Nitto Co.Ltd, which was founded in Tokyo Japan in 1950. Naigai Nitto offers a full range of logistics transportation and supply chain ranging from International freight forwarding by sea and air, land transportation to warehousing and distrbution.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will handle key warehouse operations including receiving, checking, scanning, picking, packing, loading, and unloading cargoes to ensure accurate and efficient logistics processes.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Verify incoming cargoes against packing lists and import/export instructions to ensure shipment accuracy</li><li>Enter inventory data and conduct stock takes to maintain accurate warehouse records</li><li>Scan, pick, and pack cargoes following packing list instructions to prepare shipments correctly</li><li>Load and unload cargoes safely to support timely transportation and delivery</li><li>Perform additional warehouse tasks as assigned to support overall operations</li></ul><p>Requirements:<br /></p><ul><li>Knowledgeable in excel and microsoftword</li><li>Possess forklift licence is an added advantage</li><li>Able to carry heavy cargoes up to 20kg.</li><li>Fresh school leavers with no experience are welcome to apply.</li></ul>",
